Why IECF

The #1 platform worldwide dedicated to education, training, culture, innovation, creativity, & career development. This groundbreaking platform serves as a comprehensive hub that seamlessly connects educational pathways with relevant career opportunities across various main and sub-disciplines.

Why Egypt

Egypt is an ideal choice to organize the biggest international event and platform for education, training, talent, creativity, innovation, and career due to several reasons:
1. Unparalleled history
2. Market size
3. Strategic location
